description: This is an entry point source file for a React application. It imports necessary modules, including React, ReactDOM, CSS styles, and the main App component. It creates the root DOM node and renders the App component within React’s StrictMode for highlighting potential problems during development.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
